    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>Re ''Progressive, Conservative or Rock Star?,'' by Kenneth L. Woodward (Op-Ed, April 11):</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>Re ''Progressive, Conservative or Rock Star?,'' by Kenneth L. Woodward (Op-Ed, April 11):</p>
        <p>It is my hope that a new pope will understand that a truly vibrant ''Gospel of Life'' must include family planning to help eliminate poverty and the use of safe-sex birth control to eradicate the scourge of AIDS.</p>
        <p>It is also my fervent prayer that a new pope will understand that science can be used for the betterment of man's condition and that stem cell research may well be an essential element to save human life.</p>
        <p>Natalie Burrows  Brooklyn, April 11, 2005</p>
      </block>
